OL,7,FAround 100,000 civil servants are on
OL,8,Fstrike in a one-day walkout over pay,
OL,9,Fpensions, cuts and redundancy terms.
OL,11,FMembers of the Public and Commercial
OL,12,FServices Union (PCS) across 124
OL,13,Fgovernment departments voted to strike
OL,14,Fin a 2022 union ballot.
OL,16,FThe union says that a further 33,000
OL,17,Funion members in five more government
OL,18,Fdepartments, including HMRC, Companies
OL,19,FHouse, Care Quality Commission, and the
OL,20,FWelsh Government are re-balloting next
OL,21,Fweek to take industrial action.
